my own but tired

02:10.103 --> 02:39.925
I've

02:10.103 --> 02:39.925
learned one thing from how we were That an ounce of 
prevention's worth about a cure The shadows fall

02:10.103 --> 02:39.925
but I cannot threaten Los palabristas estamos a 
